<div id="about-the-community" class="section-spacer">
    <h2 class="sect-title">About Shawnee Slopes</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-xl">Named after the early Shawnee settlers, the community in Shawnee Slopes is a mature and
                well planned neighborhood that has a lot to offer to the young families and working professionals
                looking for starter homes and apartments. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">The Shawnee Slopes Real Estate is situated right along the Fish Creek Park and offers
                access to a plethora of modern amenities barely a few minutes away.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">Homes for sale in Shawnee Slopes are readily available for a starting price of around
                $200,000 with the high end properties being listed at around the early 800s.</p>
        </div>
